# ── WORKSPACE workspace hardening ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Extra belt-and-braces to keep real accounting data out of this OSS repo.
# The orchestrator in `../firma-orchestrator/orchestrator/` is what reads real
# data; this exporter is treated as a pure code library.
.env.*
config.local.toml
config.*.toml
!config.example.toml
*.key
*.pem
*.pfx
# Any real data checked in by mistake under tests/fixtures/
tests/fixtures/real_*
tests/fixtures/**/real_*
# Invoice / receipt / statement PDFs should never be in the repo
*.pdf
!docs/**/*.pdf
# CSVs outside examples
*.csv
!tests/fixtures/*.csv
!config/**/*.csv
!examples/**/*.csv

